  "body": "Tried with solc 0.8.3:\r\n\r\n```solidity\r\npragma solidity ^0.8.0;\r\n\r\ncontract Test {\r\n    uint[type(uint16).max] test;\r\n}\r\n```\r\n\r\nAnd got this:\r\n\r\n```\r\n$ solc-0.8.3 Test.sol\r\nError: Invalid array length, expected integer literal or constant expression.\r\n --> Test.sol:4:10:\r\n  |\r\n4 |     uint[type(uint16).max] test;\r\n  |          ^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^\r\n```",
